page.title: 03Lifestyle of a schoolboy SAT
page.content: Although I go to bed quite late in the evening I usually wake up about 7:00am to 7:30am and have breakfast.This gives me plenty of time to get ready for Tennis Club at St.Austell which starts at 10:00am.After I have had my breakfast I usually turn my computer on and play some games on it-"Match Point"which is a game in which you have to beat your opponent at tennis. After this I go to get dressed,I put on my tennis whites,my tracksuit,and my socks and "PUMA" trainers,pick up my raquet,and am driven off to my tennis match.When this is finished I go home to have lunch and finish my homework .I then watch the television until my bedtime.
